title: Editor looking for master to challenger player for collaboration
body:
Hello there!
I am looking for a master or challenger player interested in a collaboration to create a really good youtube channel , depending on the personality of the player it may vary the style of the editing but mostly trying to give really good advices to lower helo players and keep updating with news patches and champs following the trend of other youtubers but of course creating also something innovative.
If interest contact me at my email

Cheers guys
